TY  - JOUR
T1  - Epidemic Exposure, Financial Technology, and the Digital Divide
AU  - SAKA, ORKUN
AU  - EICHENGREEN, BARRY
AU  - AKSOY, CEVAT GIRAY
Y1  - 2022/10/01
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2022/10/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/jmcb.12945
